    <string name="problems">Problems with times?</string>
    <string name="incorrect_times_html"><![CDATA[Sometimes the times at the stops don\'t match the ones in the app.  This is because the times on the luas website are wrong and that is where this app gets the times from.  You can <a href=\'http://m.luas.ie/contactus\'>report the error to them</a> and they will be able to fix it.]]></string>
    <string name="missing_times_html"><![CDATA[When the app shows no times it can be for a few reasons.  There might be a problem with the timing system and you can verify this by <a href=\'http://m.luas.ie/live-info/\'>checking the luas site</a>.  Alternatively it may be because there is <a href=\'http://m.luas.ie/travel-updates.html\'>an incident on the line</a>.]]></string>
    <string name="other_problem_html"><![CDATA[If you are still having issues after checking the above then please <a href=\'mailto:mbcdroid@gmail.com\'>send me an email</a> with as much detail about the issue as you can provide.]]></string>
